'''Phindar Spaceport''' was the major [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] of [[Phindar/Legends|Phindar]]. It had a [[Gravity/Legends|gravity]] of 0.69g.

During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] along with Jedi Knights [[Maks Leem]] and [[Jai Maruk]], as well as their respective apprentices [[Whie Malreaux/Legends|Whie Malreaux]] and [[Tallisibeth Enwandung-Esterhazy]]&mdash;nicknamed "Scout"&mdash;visited Phindar Spaceport on their secret mission to [[Vjun/Legends|Vjun]]. Soon after their arrival, they were ambushed by [[Asajj Ventress/Legends|Asajj Ventress]] and several [[Droid/Legends|droids]], which resulted in the [[Death/Legends|deaths]] of Maks Leem and Jai Maruk.

